Budget Planning Guide

Annual Cybersecurity Budget Breakdown (Healthcare):
- Tools & Technology: 40-50%
	- Security software
	- Hardware (firewalls, etc.)
	- Cloud services
- Personnel: 30-40%
	- Security staff salaries
	- Training and development
	- Consultants/MSSP
- Compliance & Audit: 10-15%
	- Certifications
	- Audits
	- Legal counsel
- Training & Awareness: 5-10%
	- Training programs
	- Phishing simulations
	- Materials and campaigns
Typical Healthcare Organization:
- Small clinic (< 50 staff): €20,000 - €50,000/year
- Medium hospital (50-500 staff): €100,000 - €500,000/year
- Large hospital (500+ staff): €500,000 - €2,000,000+/year
Note: Percentages of IT budget typically range from 5-15% depending on maturity

