B.2 Employee Offboarding Security Checklist

```
EMPLOYEE NAME: _______________  DEPARTMENT: _______________
LAST DAY: _______________      MANAGER: _______________
REASON: □ Resignation  □ Termination  □ Retirement  □ Other

□ NOTIFICATION RECEIVED:
  Date notified: _______________
  Security team notified: _______________
  
□ IMMEDIATE ACTIONS (For Termination):
  □ Disable accounts immediately
  □ Revoke physical access (badge deactivated)
  □ Revoke remote access (VPN)
  □ Change passwords for shared accounts
  □ Alert security team for monitoring
  □ Escort from premises if required
  
□ SCHEDULED ACTIONS (Resignation/Retirement):
  □ Knowledge transfer completed
  □ Access reduced to needed only
  □ Increased monitoring active
  
□ LAST DAY:
  □ All system access disabled (COB)
  □ Email account disabled
  □ VPN access revoked
  □ Mobile device wiped/returned
  □ Laptop/computer returned
  □ Badge returned
  □ Keys returned
  □ Parking pass returned
  □ Security tokens returned
  □ Any company data on personal devices removed
  □ Exit interview security reminders given
  □ NDA/confidentiality reminder
  □ Return of property receipt signed
  
□ WITHIN 24 HOURS:
  □ Verify all access revoked
  □ Remove from distribution lists
  □ Update phone directories
  □ Remove from physical access systems
  □ Archive email per policy
  □ Transfer file ownership
  □ Remove from security groups
  □ Remove from collaboration tools
  
□ WITHIN 1 WEEK:
  □ Final access verification audit
  □ Certificate revocation confirmed
  □ Cloud account access removed
  □ Third-party system access removed
  □ Final documentation completed
  
□ WITHIN 30 DAYS:
  □ Account deletion (per retention policy)
  □ Final security review
  □ Close all tickets/requests
  
NOTES/SPECIAL CONSIDERATIONS:
_________________________________________________
_________________________________________________

COMPLETED BY: _______________  DATE: _______________
VERIFIED BY: _______________   DATE: _______________

```

